{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f25f4df3db","title":"和邹春培先生应对联（之一）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bd8d4d091b","index":0,"year":1902,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"f25f4df3db"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji1","name":"毛泽东全集第1卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3684da21d7","type":"paragraph","text":"和邹春培先生应对联（之一）","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"f25f4df3db"},{"id":"072e5020c8","type":"paragraph","text":"（1902年）灌足：（邹春培）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"f25f4df3db"},{"id":"4c8285437c","type":"paragraph","text":"修身。（毛泽东）[1]这是毛泽东和私熟先生的应对联。1902年春，毛泽东从居家托外祖父家回都山，入南岸私垫读书，启蒙老师是部春培。一天，邹春培先生图事外出，强学生费书。但是，先生回馆一看，却见毛泽东和儿个孩子在塘中戏水。先生好生气临，把毛泽东和几个孩子叫到跟前，指着他们的泥已脚了子，念出上联要他们对，对得好，可免于打板子，毛泽东灵机一动，脱口对出了下联。先生听了，不禁暗暗点头赞贝。邻春培，1902年春至1904年秋，毛泽东在韶山南岸私整读书时的老师。灯光。少年毛泽东的卧室。毛泽东常在晚上把门窗遮起来念书，不让父亲看到","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"f25f4df3db"},{"id":"d1ada15dc4","type":"paragraph","text":"1903韶山毛氏宗祠。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"f25f4df3db"}],"page":{"id":"53835b6aee","publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"f25f4df3db","start":67,"end":70}}}},"__N_SSG":true}